영문물품설명: Metal 3D printers for customized production of metal materials for various uses are equipment that melts various metals into precious metals (rings, brooches, various decorations, etc.), medical (teeth prostheses, artificial joints, jaw joints, facial cheekbones, etc.), industrial (space Airlines, automobiles, molds, etc.)All metal three-dimensional molded products have been used as main processes by creating a shape frame and pouring and casting molten metal according to the frame and cutting processing of metal materials by milling using a 3D CAD. MERAIN Co., Ltd. The processing method of a three-dimensional molded product by a metal 3D printer DAVID1.0 completes the three-dimensional molded product by thinly laying 14㎛~40㎛ of metal powder, such as flour, at 30㎛ on a vertically operated base, melting the metal powder with a laser, and stacking a further layer according to input 3D modeling. In this way, it is possible to manufacture high-temperature bearings that cannot be assembled, and precise spaces or installations inside can also be implemented.This metal 3D printer consists of laser devices of different capacities depending on the size of the molded article, scanners that help operate, computers and monitors that connect command systems, dust collectors that cleanly regenerate fume generated inside the printer chamber, and various electrical safety devices.
영문업체설명: MERAIN Co., Ltd. is a company specializing in developing and manufacturing metal 3D printers of the PBF (Power Bed Fusion) type. DAVID1.0, which can output metal 3D products with high functionality and low price with a 300W output laser and a 120Diameter x 100mm height through the Additive Manufacturing (AM) process, will present convenience to customers.

영문물품설명: Vitamin Lamp is the first product developed based on the HS FRAME technology, and it is designed to replace the general lamp used in the outdoor lighting. Until now, entire street lighting facility had to be replaced to install an LED lamp. Now, all you need to do is keep the lighting facility and just replace the lamp, pure and simple. The Vitamin Lamp is evaluated as providing the highest performance for over three years.LED lighting reduces energy consumption up to 70%. It is an eco-friendly lighting with 5 times longer life span than the conventional lighting. LED lighting was introduced 20 years ago but the market penetration has not yet reached 20%.The LED technology limitation on heat problem is at the center of the slow adoption of LED lighting. The heat problem was resolved for indoor lighting and now it is possible to simply replace the bulb. Outdoor lighting, however, generates 40 times more heat to generate 20 times brighter light than indoor light. It means an existing lighting facility must be removed and a new lighting facility must be installed. For this reason, the cost of replacing the facility is higher than the price of a LED lamp and the high cost has created a big problem in adopting LED lighting. So, the remaining 80% of the market has not converted to LED and end up purchasing 30% of regular lighting fixtures every year.At BKT, we have come up with HS FRAME technology and solved the central age-old LED issue.Our technology is based on the semiconductor lead frame process and integrated LED chip, PCB and heat sink into the single HS FRAME. HS FRAME has a simplified design that transfers heat and current without solder, releases heat 10 times faster and maintains 30% lower temperature.In the case of conventional LED technology we have replaced, LED chip, PCB and heat sink are separated from each other. Also, heat generated from the current is transferred through adhesion using soldier.The old technology creates a heat bottleneck due to the inefficient, complex heat transfer structure. In contrast, HS FRAME releases heat more than 10 times faster and maintains 30% lower temperature through a structure that provides current without solder and releases heat by itself.In general, solder connects the components and circuits and supplies current. In LED lighting, it is a key material that transfers heat as well as current. But, solder has not only a low thermal conductivity but also is sensitive to temperature change. Solder often breaks because its volume expands at lower temperature and causes a durability issue for the product.Moreover, the fact that a bulky, heavy heat sink is eliminated is key to creating ultra-thin and lightweight lighting products with 2 times longer lifespan through efficient thermal management.As you can see, our HS FRAME technology has not only improved the LED technology and product performance, it allowed us to simplify the production process and reduce the cost by 50%.
영문업체설명: BKT’s Vitamin Lamp is a high-intensity discharge (HID) outdoor lamp used for street, park, security, and tunnel lighting. Our lamp offers 50%-70% energy savings and 10 times longer lifespan relative to the conventional non-LED lamp. It offers 3 times greater wattage output, 30% greater thermal and light efficiencies, and 5 times lighter in weight relative to the conventional LED lamp.

영문물품설명: HI-WARE is IAM (Identity and Access Management) solution which consists of two module-HI-TAM and HI-TIM.HI-TAM is Access Management solution of HI-WARE. HI-TAM controls and manages remote access of IT system like network, server, etc., sets prohibited command to prevent misuse by user, monitors users’ session on real time, and creates as audit logs.HI-TAM can strengthen security by preventing unnecessary access and human errors in advance, secure transparency in details of works through audit log, and quickly solve system failure. HI-TIM is Identity Management solution of HI-WARE. HI-TIM interworks with HR(Human Resource) system, integrates and manages all users accounts. HI-TIM provides account life cycle management like create/modify/delete account through workflow, and automatically detects illegal accounts like inactive accounts, ghost accounts, etc. then serves a notice to system manager and locks illegal accounts. In addition, HI-TIM prevents password leaks by providing an automatic/semi-automatic log-in and automatic password change function in a regular way according to a company’s policy.

영문물품설명: An elevator or lift is a type of vertical transportation that moves people or goods between floors of a building, vessel, or other structure. Machine room-less elevators are designed so that most of the components fit within the shaft containing the elevator car; and a small cabinet houses the elevator controller. Other than the machinery being in the hoistway, the equipment is similar to a normal traction or hole-less hydraulic elevator. The benefits are:1. Creates more usable space2. Use less energy (70-80% less than standard hydraulic elevators)3. Uses no oil (assuming it is a traction elevator)4. All components are above ground similar to roped hydraulic type elevators (this takes away the environmental concern that was created by the hydraulic cylinder on direct hydraulic type elevators being stored underground)5. Slightly lower cost than other elevators; significantly so for the hydraulic MRL elevator6. Can operate at faster speeds than hydraulics but not normal traction units.

영문물품설명:
BIO-Sp's Ansen PP Roll Sheet Lining Technological Outline

1. Since the base material is Polypropylene(PP) which is used even for sanitary items, this product is verified to have multiple purposes.
2. BioSP was the world’s first company to successfully develop a
PPbased material sheet lining that can be installed in a large
scale fresh water tank.
3. This product excels in problematic areas such scratches on the
surfaces and tensile force problems that a comparative product
(HDPE) faces.
4. PP sheets does not have a glossy surface or scratches due to the
temperature control from the heating manufacturing process and
minimized damages on the surface from cleaning
5. PP based sheet lining technoligy can immediately store and supply
water upon construction.
6. Even if water is supplied shortly after construction there is no odor
formed like that from ceramic or epoxy coatings, and its safety is
reassured with its coefficient of moisture absorption being 0.05%
which allows an anti-bacterial effect preventing bacteria to grow.
7. With patented technology of deaeration between the sheet and the concrete stabilizing air pressure, the problems resulting from condensation of external water is fixed.
8. Even if there are cracks in the concrete due to external factors, the sheet can withhold a waterproof layer without any damage.
9. Unlike ceramic or epoxy layers PP is not painted on, therefore when
applied the thickness is constant throughout all the surfaces allowing
optimum performance.
10. There is no leakage of catalysts(phthalic acid and isocyanide).
11. It is a non-toxic material with low levels of chlorine gas and
resistant to ozone, chloride, weather, cold, chemicals and corrosion.
12. It can sustain a semi-permanent effect with one construction.
13. Easier and cheaper maintenance with optimal coefficient of elasticity
which prevents cracks.
14. We are certified company as Goverment Excellent Product by Korea
PPS(Public Procurement Service) and obtained certification KC(Korea
Certification), Green Cretification as well as many patents including
PCT.
영문업체설명: BioSP Co., Ltd. is a eco-friendly company. PP based sheet lining technoligy can immediately store and supply water upon construction. We are certified company as Goverment Excellent Product by Korea    PPS(Public Procurement Service) and obtained certification KC(Korea    Certification), Green Cretification as well as many patents including    PCT.

영문물품설명: Y, B, D, T, C(S) - STRAINER ELEMENT ( SCREEN )STRAINERIt is a device mounted on a pipe line of various plants and systems for removingimpurities or protecting the equipment on which mounted.Each device is to be made into the one with proper shape depending on its purpose.Fluid : Oil, Gas, Water, Chemical, ETC.Type Y : IS for the purpose of removing inside impurities of andprotecting             equipments of various valves, nozzles of installations, traps and             pump suction.Type B : Is suitable for the fluid with high viscosity such as liquid raw             material or B-C oil and used widely when enough surface area              of filtration is required due to a large amount of foreign substances             from the pump suction which is large-capacity, or used for water             treatment.Type D : Has filtration screens mounted on both sides(left and right) and             they can change the direction of fluid flow to either side.             Then, the screen through which the fluid doesn't flow can remove             foreign substances.             Type D is used where fluid flow of a pipe in operation should not             be cut off.Type T : Has more advantages in effective area and pressure loss than the            Type Y.            In case of angle flow, it is unnecessary to install elbow, so it can            reduce the cost.            It is possible to choose the direction of fluid flow depending on the            purpose.Type C(S) : Is used in test working of pipe line. It is general to disassemble                  it after regular inspection, but recently it is used permanently in                  a line where foreign substances hardly be made such as                  compress suction or LNG.

영문물품설명:
BentoTex (Bentonite Mat)

BentoTex is geosynthetic clay liner (GCL) consisting of a thin layer of low permeable sodium bentonite and two layers of geotextile: PP woven fabric and PP non-woven fabric. Three layers are needle punched together to increase shear resistance. BentoTex has been proved to provide engineering performance and durability better than several feet thick compacted clay or a quarter inch thick bentonite admixed with soil. BentoTex, highly impermeable barrier, is frequently used as liner of environmental containment, pond and river. It is an alternative to traditional compacted clay liner.

Use
- Preventing soil pollution from landfill leachate
- Liner for artificial water way, lake, pond, and water hazard
- Exterior waterproofing and protection for underground structures such as building basement, tunnel, underground car park, and water tank


Characteristics
- When bentonite layer confined is hydrated, it is not able to swell free but renders incomplete underground structures or workmanship in terms of waterproofing completed, owing to 4 kinds of self finish as abbreviated to 4S
*4S: Self-adhering to structure surface, Self-detailing corners, Self- seaming overlapped joints of bentonite sheets, and Self-sealing minor cracks of structures
- Installation of bentonite is faster, more cost-effective, and more hygienic than that of bentonite admixed with soil, that requires large earth work and produces dust during mixing bentonite and soil
Defective installation can be checked by simple visual inspection

① Permanent waterproofing performance: no deterioration even after severe freeze-thaw or wet-dry cycles. Natural inorganic mineral bentonite that is hardly degraded
② Simple, fast, eco-friendly construction: installation by simple joint overlap, least construction defects and non-hazardous substance
③ All-weather construction: installation enabled even on wet surface and under cold weather
④ Simple quality control: visual inspection is sufficient
⑤ Simple repair by filling defective area with granular bentonite

Products
BentoTex-S : Standard product for waste landfill and environmental containments
BentoTex-LS : For pond, river, and waterway
BentoTex-SW : For landfill, environmental containments under saline environment
BentoTex-K : For underground structure, shafts, car pass, and subway
BentoTex-BE : For landfill and environmental containments where leachate needs to be purified

영문물품설명: BentoSeal (Bentonite joint sealing materialUnlike conventional water stop, BentoSeal exerts perfect and permanent water stop even in the level of high ground water. The main material of BentoSeal is natural sodium bentonite swelling about 15~20 times its original volume when it absorbs water. Installation is very simple and fast.Use- Water stop of horizontal or vertical construction joint for underground structure such as basement, cut and cover tunnel, parking lot, and water tank- Water stop supplement at such horizontal or vertical penetrations as pipe, duct, and pile head of structureCharacteristic- 4S effect is displayed when it is hydrated with water in concrete but not able to swell free in confined state*4S: Self-adhering to structure surface, Self-detailing corners, Self-seaming overlapped joints of bentonite sheets, and Self-sealing minor cracks of structures- Easy and fast to install in place① Permanent water stop: natural inorganic mineral bentonite which is hardly degradable results in, no deterioration of its function② Simple, fast, eco-friendly construction: installation simpler and faster than water stop based on rubber and synthetic resin

영문물품설명:
BentoSheet (Bentonite Sheet)

BentoSheet is a composite waterproofing product which is one of geosynthetic clay liners (GCL) consisting of two layers: low permeability sodium bentonite layer and HDPE (high density polyethylene) geomembrane. It provides a highly impermeable barrier and so has been used as waterproofing material for underground structure, tunnel, shafts, boxes, building basement, replacing a variety of traditional membrane waterproofing sheet.

Use
Exterior waterproofing and protection for underground structures such as building basement, cut and cover tunnel, underground car park, and water tank

Characteristics
- When bentonite layer confined is hydrated, it is not able to swell free but renders incomplete underground
structures or workmanship completed, that is 4 kinds of self finish as abbreviated to 4S
*4S: Self-adhering to structure surface, Self-detailing corners, Self-seaming overlapped joints of bentonite sheets, and Self-sealing minor cracks of structures
- Easy and quick installation simply by nailing
- Reduction of risk for punctures and leakage
- No water leaks in the membrane at common chronic problems such as debonding → capillary phenomenon
→ leaking processes. Even though there is defect, it is easy to repair
Low defects, easy to check by visual inspection

Permanent waterproofing performance: no deterioration even after severe freeze-thaw, wet-dry cycles.
Natural inorganic mineral bentonite that is not degradable
② Double waterproofing system: primary impermeable HDPE layer, bentonite layer
③ Simple, fast, all-weather, eco-friendly construction: minimum preparation, fixing with nail without primer or adhesive, installation even on wet surface and under cold weather, simple joint overlap
④ Reduction of installation cost and time
⑤ Proper installation can be assured by simple visual inspection
⑥ Simple repair due to no capillary phenomenon

Products
BentoSheet-S : Standard product for external wall of underground structure
BentoSheet-SW : For external wall in saline environments
BentoSheet-BH : Standard BentoSheet reinforced by with non-woven textile

영문물품설명:
This product consists of steel pipe(inside) and complex PPB pipe(outside).
Complex PPB pipe makes to prevent corrosion and an electric leakage even
contact with cement or water.

Heat Transfer speed

Inside pipe is filled with magnesia before compression. Heat transfer speed of
magnesia is three times faster than water.

Maximization of heat efficiency

As it is designed to seal the space between complex PPB exterior pipe and inner pipe. it excels in secondary heat diffusion speed and heat storage.

Non-electromagnetic wave
It is Korea's only non-electromagnetic wave sheath heater based on offsetting design of heating element(spring-type/double track design).

Power saving type
As a double track is applied to heating element, the product excels in heat efficiency. It is a power-saving sheath heater electric ONDOL that can implement heating with 400W/hr/3.3m²
영문업체설명: Since establishment in 1997, Have been manufactured electric Ondol. Electric Ondol is a kind of under-floor heating system that heats the floor by using the electricity. We are getting reputation as the specialized in this field in Korea. We have been exporting to Japan, Russia and Kazakhstan and try to expand overseas market.

영문물품설명: Sterilization and purification functions of Plasma UV Sterilizing LampThe plasma UV sterilizing lamp is inserted in the titanium dioxide photocatalyst tube. The lamp generates strong OH radical with strong oxidation and has far better oxidizing power than chlorine or ozone and the maximum array (eight) structure so that it completely destroys pollutants in the air.he complex function of sterilization, deodorization, and purificationThe product removes pollutants in the way of oxidation-reduction reaction, not simply in the way of filtering. Therefore, it not only removes the secondary contamination possibility, but has the complex function of sterilizing, deodorizing, and purifying harmful bacteria, chemical materials, fine dust, and odors.Multiple-layer & complex filtering system excellent in anti-bacterial and sterilizing functions and in the removal of harmful materials and odorsBy applying multiple-layer & complex filtering system, the product resolves volatile organic compounds, and removes acidic smelly gases like formaldehyde, the cause of sick house syndrome, basic odors like the living odor ammonia, and various harmful bacteria in order to optimize the indoor air quality.Economic air sterilizing purifier with minimum power consumption, low maintenance cost, and high purifying efficiencyAlong with long-term or semi-permanent available filter, the plasma UV sterilizing lamp, which has cooling and heating structure with low heat in the type of External Electrode Fluorescent Lamp, not general fluorescent lamp, helps to not only lower maintenance cost and power consumption, but keep producing sterilizing effect.Technologically approved product through domestic and foreign certificatesThe 7-step purification technology of the plasma UV sterilizing lamp was approved by Korea Ozone UV Association (PA certificate), Korea Testing Laboratory (K Mark), Public Procurement Service (Good procurement), and by European Union (CE Mark). And its patent was registered (patent no. 10-0946106). The corporate research institute ceaselessly performs R&D and expands R&B to develop and produce high-quality products.

영문물품설명:
Hasuh Pump Gate (HPG) series has been developed as a new drainage facility that integrates the pump and the gate into one system.
The system consists of screen, gate leaf, actuator, submersible pump, flap valve and local control panel.
It does not require large scale sump pit area and pump station work.
As no sump pit and pumping station are required, no area for them are required.
As pump is integrally equipped with gate, it’s very simple and easy to maintain the pump.
As it is simple to install pump gate, it takes only short time to construct the system.
To compare the ordinary pump station with pump gate in terms of cost, great reduction can be achieved.
When exterior water level goes higher than that of interior water, Screen and Pump Gate will be completely closed in order to prevent exterior water from flowing back into the interior water and to prepare the pump operation.
If interior water level reaches to the predetermined water level, Pump and Screen will be automatically operated in order to discharge interior water forcibly toward outside through gate.
When exterior water level drops lower than that of interior water, Pump Gate and Screen will be opened so that interior water will flow naturally toward outside.
영문업체설명: Hasuh Industries Corporation, as a leading company in the field of flood control industry in Korea, has successfully completed as many as 49 pump gate projects in the domestic markets. In addition, we have been proud of successful operation in the two projects at Jakarta (2010) and Bali (2013) respectively in Indonesia.   We have devoted our best efforts to innovation and assurance of quality which will result in the supply of the best value to our customers since its establishment in 2001.

영문물품설명: Gate opens automatically when water overflow is detectedWhen it rains or there is water overflow, the inner gate of the system automatically detects thepressure and opens to drain the water.Cover automatically opens during heavy rains and floodingWhen the drainage channel overflows due to heavy rain or flooding, the upper cover of the system detects the pressure and automatically opens to a degree appropriate to the level of overflow. The cover then closes after the water level returns to normal, preventing additional problems from overflow.Gate closes automaticallyWhen it is not in operation, the gate automatically closes to prevent unpleasant odors and insectpopulations.Cover detaches as neededThe S-hinge structure of the cover makes it detachable, allowing for easier maintenance andremoval of sewage and inner dirt.No more theftTraditional casted-metal grates and drain covers can be stolen easily, making them difficult tomanage and maintain, while our plastic grating system is free from such worries.No more lost personal belongingsItems such as mobile phones or keys cannot fall into the automated grating system, meaningcitizens do not need to worry about losing important personal belongings. Also, when items dofall into the grating system, they are easy to find and remove.
